<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[[جصص]</span>]<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الجِصُّ والجَصُّ:</span> ما يبنَى به، وهو معرّب.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">ووالجَصَّاً:</span> الذي يتَّخذه.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وجَصَّصَ دارَه، مثل قَصَّصَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وجَصَّصَ الجروُ:</span> فَتَحَ عينيه، مثل بَصَّصَ وبَصْبَصَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>